surf s1000   sqc      0.0 0.0 158.5
surf top     pz       182.88
surf z1      pz       0.0
surf bottom  pz      -182.88

cell c1000  0 fill uCore     -s1000     bottom -z1
cell c1001  0 fill uCore     -s1000     z1 -top
cell c1100  0 outside        -bottom 
cell c1101  0 outside         top 
cell c1102  0 outside         s1000    bottom -top 
